{"word":"H2372 - חָזָה - châzâh - khaw-zaw' - Behold","slug":"H2372","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָזָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châzâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-zaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D6;&#x05D4; - cha&#x0302;za&#x0302;h</b> - <i>khaw-zaw</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>gaze</i> at; mentally to <i>perceive</i>, <i>contemplate</i> (with pleasure); specifically to <i>have a vision of: - </i>behold, look, prophesy, provide, see."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2335\">H2335</a>, <a href=\"#/H2371\">H2371</a>, <a href=\"#/H2374\">H2374</a>, <a href=\"#/H2377\">H2377</a>, <a href=\"#/H2378\">H2378</a>, <a href=\"#/H2380\">H2380</a>, <a href=\"#/H2381\">H2381</a>, <a href=\"#/H2382\">H2382</a>, <a href=\"#/H2383\">H2383</a>, <a href=\"#/H2384\">H2384</a>, <a href=\"#/H3166\">H3166</a>, <a href=\"#/H3167\">H3167</a>, <a href=\"#/H4236\">H4236</a>, <a href=\"#/H4237\">H4237</a>, <a href=\"#/H4238\">H4238</a>"}]}